-- Omega Advisors sold firm's 1.1 mln SeaWorld shares '3 weeks ago' -sources
-- 
-- Thu Aug 14, 2014 03:29PM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, Aug 14 (Reuters) - Leon Cooperman's Omega Advisors sold all of the firm's 1.1 million share stake in SeaWorld Entertainment <SEAS.N> "three weeks ago," two sources familiar with the matter said on Thursday.     (Reporting By Jennifer Ablan; Editing by Chris Reese)  ((jennifer.ablan@thomsonreuters.com;))  Keywords: INVESTING OMEGA/SEAWORLD ENTRNMT

